Municipal Impact: None
Explanation
The resolution results in a potential cost to the state by rehearing the
claim of Evan Clark, PPA, Christopher Clark. The associated fiscal
impact depends on the adjudication of the claim.
The Out Years
Based on the timing of when the claim is potentially awarded, and
since it would be one-time in nature, there would be no out year fiscal
impact.
